00:01:14.868 --> 00:01:19.228
<i>Svako stanje ima poseban</i>
<i>ton i posebno vidljivo svetlo.</i>

00:01:20.371 --> 00:01:22.083
<i>U noći, 20-og aprila</i>

00:01:22.284 --> 00:01:25.197
<i>da li ste čuli neki od tih</i>
<i>alarma na Dipvoter Horajzonu?</i>

00:01:25.398 --> 00:01:26.706
<i>Ne gospodine.</i>

00:01:26.720 --> 00:01:27.920
<i>PO ISTINITOM DOGAĐAJU</i>

00:01:27.982 --> 00:01:31.042
<i>Da li znate zašto nikad</i>
