platformi je loš da ne može biti lošiji.

00:12:17.052 --> 00:12:19.496
Vredi koliko i sujeverje.

00:12:20.606 --> 00:12:22.278
Ime?
-Majk Vilijams.

00:12:22.479 --> 00:12:24.647
Gde idete danas?
-Dipvoter Horajzon.

00:12:41.876 --> 00:12:43.419
Šta radiš u slobodno vreme?

00:12:44.215 --> 00:12:47.227
Ah ponovo počeo da radim na brodu.
-Da?

00:12:47.428 --> 00:12:51.020
Dižem ga sa 600ks na 1.200.

00:12:51.621 --> 00:12:55.559
I nabavio sam mali Sensenik propeler.

00:12:55.760 --> 00:12:59.042
Pokušavaš da poletiš?
-Ne, samo hoću da ide brže.

00:13:06.635 --> 00:13:08.883
<i>Čisto?</i>
<i>-Primio, imam sve.</i>

00:13:09.084 --> 00:13:12.504
<i>Boskou, imam Dipvoterove</i>
<i>koordinate u FMS.</i>

00:13:12.706 --> 00:13:15.494
<i>492, rep ti je čist. Vetar je miran.</i>

00:13:40.747 --> 00:13:43.448
<i>Pariz kontroli, ovo je Bristou 2 Bravo Gou</i>

00:13:43.549 --> 00:13:45.307
<i>Idemo na otvoreni okean.</i>

00:13:45.509 --> 00:13:48.303
<i>Očekivano vreme dolaska</i>
<i>na Dipvoter Horajzon, 45 minuta.</i>

00:13:48.505 --> 00:13:50.873
<i>Primio, Bristou 2 Bravo Gou.</i>

00:13:51.174 --> 00:13:53.575
Šta radite u Britiš Petrolu, g. Sims?

00:13:53.776 --> 00:13:56.378
Zadovoljan.
